<span class="postbody">I have been pleased with my <a href="http://www.ati.com/products/radeon9550/specs.html" target="_blank" class="postlink">ATI Radeon 9550</a>, which I think is in about the same clase as the BFG card.  I know you said you were happy with NVIDIA, and I was too.  In fact, I think I upgraded from the same sort of card you had.  Seems to run WoW great (I am afraid the house rules now prohibit me from comparing how it runs eq or eq2 =\).  Anyway, the one I got had 256 mb memory, and cost about $120.  Good deal.   I've got 640 mb of RAM and i want to upgrade to 1 gig.  I'm planning on using the coupon that came with EQ2 to get a discount at kingston.com, when I feel like shelling out the extra dough.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
