<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Generally the FX series of Nvidia cards were total crap.  Their performance on DX9 games was sub-par to the equally priced ATI cards (with even worse Image Quality).  So I would look into ATi if I were you.
<br />

<br />
Now if you were going to spend the Money on a next gen card, I would say go Nvidia.  The 6800 Series of cards does extremely well.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Of course if the cycle continues like it has, when the next generation of cards come out ATI will take the title.. Only to lose it to Nvidia on the cards after that.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
